caption:
This privately gated French Country estate in North Ranch Country Club Estates offers elegance and style on 3.04 acres.

The 12,167 sq. ft. home features 9 bedrooms, 10.5 baths, and 2,500 sq. ft. of covered outdoor space. Highlights include a grand two-story foyer with a spiral staircase, formal living and dining areas, a chef’s kitchen, a library, gym, and theater. The primary suite and guest rooms feature high ceilings and fireplaces. An elevator connects all levels, with a wine cellar, pool, spa, outdoor kitchen, and parking for 20+ cars completing the property. Stunning mountain and golf course views enhance this serene retreat, just minutes from local dining and shopping.
